Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}フィクションみたいなデイドリーム
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}劇中の沈黙を破るキスして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.13,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優柔不断もぎゅっとして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胸がしぃくるしぃくる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:02.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}予測できないトキメキ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.10,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}勇気を出してよマイダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:13.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬉しい楽しいばっかじゃない　自分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっち向いてよダーリン
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:27.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わたしの純愛に気づいて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:06.74,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜欢才算是恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.84,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怂是罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:21.55,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头脑风暴滴滴答答 选一种心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:24.01,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}云隙中一阵细雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.06,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不亚至高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:30.60,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少女心它阴晴不定 可爱且无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.15,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像杂乱无章的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:40.40,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之多少的喜欢才算是恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:44.12,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱着我直到我犯困吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.66,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像是科幻片般的白日梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.71,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲吻我 打破剧中沉默吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.13,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}优柔寡断也好 抱紧我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.80,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}胸口闷得难受好难受好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:02.63,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心动无法预测
Comment: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:06.10,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's TRUE FOOL LOVE! Hold me tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.39,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鼓起勇气来呀 My darling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:13.02,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止于欢乐和欣喜 都取决于我们自己
Comment: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:15.31,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ONCE MORE SMILE, TWICE MORE CHIME
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:18.57,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}转过来看着我吧 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:27.95,OP-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意到我纯粹的爱呀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,---------------ED---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:23.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}宇宙規模でだました今を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:28.24,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}わたし愛してみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:31.41,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}あふれ出した夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}歩幅合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:39.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}針は止まる　淡い呪いにかけられて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:44.05,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}応えはいつもすり抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}やり直したいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:52.89,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\t(640,640,\3c&HB15E4F&)\blur3}ならこんなモヤることもなくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:57.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB15E4F&\blur3}心の在り処を知りたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:01.78,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&H4685C0&\blur3}いつか終わりがあることも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:04.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&H4685C0&\blur3}分かっているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:06.28,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&H4685C0&\blur3}不和の合図も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:10.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\3c&H4685C0&}裏返して　重ねないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:14.33,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\3c&H4685C0&}こんな半端なままは嫌って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:18.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}宇宙規模でだました今を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:22.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}わたし愛してみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:25.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\t(1900,2400,\3c&HC2B44C&)}あふれ出した夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}余命いくらかの今日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:35.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}何度だって　想いを馳せていてほしんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:23.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}纵使深陷天大的谎言中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:28.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想爱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:31.41,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}夜色满溢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:33.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}配合着步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.63,0:22:39.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}时钟停摆 淡淡的诅咒缠绕着我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:44.05,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}你的反应总是在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}如果只是想重来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.43,0:22:52.89,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\t(640,640,\3c&HB15E4F&)\blur3}那你这样吊着我又是何必
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:57.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB15E4F&\blur3}我想知道我的心该放在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:01.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&H4685C0&\blur3}迟早都会迎来结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:04.57,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&H4685C0&\blur3}我早就清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.74,0:23:06.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&H4685C0&\blur3}包括那些不和的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:10.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\3c&H4685C0&}我们和好吧 别再冷战了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:14.33,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\3c&H4685C0&}我讨厌和你这样拉扯下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:18.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}纵使深陷天大的谎言中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:22.59,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想爱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:25.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\t(1900,2400,\3c&HC2B44C&)}夜色满溢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}在这个不知余年多少的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:35.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}我只想要你能让我继续思念你
